2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice        | soy-milk   |
| City         | liverpool    | venice    |
| Job           | firefighter  | bartender  |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | gospel     |
| Pet           | ferret       | snake      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | volleyball |

