2. the fan of techno is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
