.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, pomegranate
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, nurse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, gospel
2 different pets are kept: ferret, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, scooter
1. the nurse is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the dancer is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Sport      | golf    | surfing      |
| Food          | asparagus | pomegranate |
| Job           | nurse     | dancer      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
| Pet           | snake     | ferret      |
| Transport     | scooter   | bus         |

 